				<wikidot:authorName>CalamityHeart</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1973848</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>After triggering an attack, FA Smythe and FA Gompton apparently began to throw SCP-3220 at each other. According to testimony, SCP-3220 began to make its characteristic squeak with every impact after repeated throwing, and its face had also changed into a significantly happier one.</p> </blockquote> <p>Usually, it's a little bit harder to pin down the exact moment I fall in love with an anomaly.</p> <p>Not with this one. :) Hearty +1!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
