				<wikidot:authorName>Zyn</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1404533</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Hearty +1 from me; the revised draft was a real treat to read. I'm glad you decided to let the pillow live, and the new additions make it extremely cute. Reminds me of when my friends and I used to hold pillow fights at each other's houses (we ended up using the pillows to bat a teddy bear back and forth, we even named each other's &quot;special moves&quot;).</p> <p>All in all, good feels all around. Nicely done!</p> 
				 	]]>
